 /kd57204JNt\n\nDetails: https://events.burlington.ca/meetings/Detail/2026-
 04-22-1300-Committee-of-Adjustment\n\nAgenda: https://burlingtonpublishing
 .escribemeetings.com/Meeting.aspx?Id=8fad4750-c6a9-4c93-aa3d-b81399df9fa0&
 Agenda=Agenda&lang=English https://events.burlington.ca/meetings/Detail/20
